      "controlledVocab": false,
      "searchable": true,
      "value": "Title taken from slide mount. View of flowers in pots and buckets on a wooden sidewalk in front of the Alyeska Resort. Hanging baskets of flowers are hanging from the deck. One woman is sitting at a picnic table underneath the deck eating, and two men are sitting in chairs near a payphone, also underneath the deck. A sign hanging from the deck reads: \"Alyeska Sport Shop.\" There are also ladders, brooms, garbage cans, hoses, watering cans, and benches underneath the deck.",
